  <main class="container container-lg py-4 pb-5 flex-grow-1">
    <h1 class="visually-hidden">Press Kit</h1>

    <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="press-about-heading">
      <h2 id="press-about-heading" class="heading-rule fs-3 fw-bold mb-3">About the organization</h2>
      <p><strong>Go Federation of the Philippines, Inc.</strong> (GoPinas) is the national federation for the game of Go in the Philippines. We promote and develop Go through member groups, school clubs, and community events, in line with our mission and vision. For full background, see <a class="content-link" href="/about/">About Us</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="press-logos-heading">
      <h2 id="press-logos-heading" class="heading-rule fs-3 fw-bold mb-3">Logo &amp; brand assets</h2>
      <p>The official downloadable press kit is available in a shared folder. Use assets as provided; do not stretch, recolor, or alter proportions.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a class="content-link" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LsCSw2AWUVyJiEYwMuAqCMY7cn2KS8BI?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download full press kit (Google Drive)</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="press-contact-heading">
      <h2 id="press-contact-heading" class="heading-rule fs-3 fw-bold mb-3">Media &amp; press contact</h2>
      <p>For interviews, statements, or asset requests, email <a class="content-link" href="mailto:bryan.chug@gofed.ph">bryan.chug@gofed.ph</a> (President).</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="press-facts-heading">
      <h2 id="press-facts-heading" class="heading-rule fs-3 fw-bold mb-3">Quick facts</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Legal name:</strong> Go Federation of the Philippines, Inc.</li>
        <li><strong>Short name:</strong> GoPinas</li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a class="content-link" href="https://gopinas.org/">gopinas.org</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
